    ObjectOrderSetStore

    public class ObjectSetStore<T extends io.aistac.common.canonical.data.ObjectBean>
extends ObjectStore<T>
    The ObjectSetStore Class is a class used to Store other objects and provide a central management class for storing Beans. Beans stored must extend ObjectBean. ObjectSetStore is an implementation of Object Store exposing only a single Map key and should be used when only a single set of related data is to be stored.
